article.description: — DeVante’ Jones had 26 points as Coastal Carolina topped South Alabama 78-65 on Friday night.
article.headline: Jones carries Coastal Carolina past South Alabama 78-65
article.linkText: Jones carries Coastal Carolina past South Alabama 78-65
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — DeVante’ Jones had 26 points as Coastal Carolina topped South Alabama 78-65 on Friday night. Garrick Green had 14 points for Coastal Carolina (8-2, 2-1 Sun Belt Conference). Deanthony Tipler added 13 points. Ebrima Dibba had 12 points. KK Curry had 19 points and nine rebounds for the Jaguars (7-5, 1-2). Michael Flowers added 16 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
